\n- **AR: `invoke` ÕæĮõ╗ż** ŌĆö ķŚ┤µÄźõŠØĶĄ¢ build’╝łķĆÜĶ┐ć publish ķā©ńĮ▓ÕÉÄńÜä endpoint’╝ē\n\n### µŚĀÕĮ▒ÕōŹńÜäń╗äõ╗Č\n\n- `PackRuntime` ŌĆö µ£¼ AR õĖŹõ┐«µö╣ pack ķĆ╗ĶŠæ\n- `PublishRuntime`ŃĆü`InvokeRuntime`ŃĆü`StatusRuntime` ŌĆö µ£¼ AR õĖŹõ┐«µö╣\n- `KubernetesProvider` / `AgentCubeProvider` ŌĆö õĖŹµČēÕÅŖ\n- Go õ║īĶ┐øÕłČÕģźÕÅŻ (`cmd/agentcube/`, `cmd/agentcube-controller/`) ŌĆö ńŗ¼ń½ŗÕ«×ńÄ░\n\n### ķŻÄķÖ®Ķ»äõ╝░\n\n| ķŻÄķÖ® | ńŁēń║¦ | ń╝ōĶ¦ŻµÄ¬µ¢Į |\n|------|------|----------|\n| Docker Õ«łµŖżĶ┐øń©ŗµ£¬Ķ┐ÉĶĪīÕ»╝Ķć┤µ×äÕ╗║Õż▒Ķ┤ź | ķ½ś | ÕēŹńĮ«µĀĪķ¬ī `_validate_build_prerequisites` µÅÉÕēŹµŻĆµ¤ź’╝īń╗ÖÕć║µĖģµÖ░ķöÖĶ»»µÅÉńż║ |\n| ńēłµ£¼Õø×µ╗ÜÕż▒Ķ┤źÕ»╝Ķć┤ metadata õĖŹõĖĆĶć┤ | õĖŁ | õĮ┐ńö©õĖ┤µŚČÕÅśķćÅõ┐ØÕŁśÕÄ¤Õ¦ŗńēłµ£¼ÕÅĘ’╝īńĪ«õ┐ØÕ╝éÕĖĖĶĘ»ÕŠäõ╣¤µē¦ĶĪīÕø×µ╗Ü |\n| Õż¦ķĢ£ÕāÅµ×äÕ╗║ĶČģµŚČµł¢ÕŹĀńö©Ķ┐ćÕżÜńŻüńøś | õĖŁ | Docker SDK stream µŚźÕ┐ŚµśŠńż║Ķ┐øÕ║”’╝øÕÉÄń╗ŁÕÅ»µĘ╗ÕŖĀńŻüńøśń®║ķŚ┤µŻĆµ¤ź |\n| õ║æń½»µ×äÕ╗║Õ╝éµŁźÕ«īµłÉ’╝īńŖČµĆüõĖŹńĪ«Õ«Ü | õĖŁ | õ║æń½»µ×äÕ╗║Ķ┐öÕø× job_id’╝īńö©µłĘķĆÜĶ┐ć `status` ÕæĮõ╗żµ¤źĶ»óµ×äÕ╗║ńŖČµĆü |\n| proxy URL µĀ╝Õ╝ÅµŚĀµĢłÕ»╝Ķć┤õŠØĶĄ¢õĖŗĶĮĮÕż▒Ķ┤ź | õĮÄ | Docker build_args õ╝ĀķĆÆ’╝īDocker Ķć¬Ķ║½õ╝ÜµŖźķöÖ’╝øÕÅ»Õ£© CLI Õ▒éÕó×ÕŖĀ URL µĀ╝Õ╝ÅµĀĪķ¬ī |\n\n## ÕżćķĆēµ¢╣µĪł\n\n### 1. BuildRuntime ń▒╗ń╝¢µÄÆµēĆµ£ēµ×äÕ╗║µŁźķ¬ż’╝łŌ£ģ ķĆēÕ«Üµ¢╣µĪł’╝ē\n\n**ÕüÜµ│Ģ**’╝Ü`BuildRuntime` ń▒╗ÕīģÕÉ½µēĆµ£ēń¦üµ£ēµ¢╣µ│Ģ’╝īÕ£© `build()` õĖŁķĪ║Õ║ÅĶ░āńö©’╝īõĖÄ `PackRuntime` µ©ĪÕ╝ÅõĖĆĶć┤ŃĆé\n\n**õ╝śńé╣**’╝Ü\n- õĖÄ AR-020 ńÜä `PackRuntime` µ×Čµ×äõĖĆĶć┤’╝īķÖŹõĮÄĶ«żń¤źĶ┤¤µŗģ\n- ķĆ╗ĶŠæķøåõĖŁ’╝īµśōõ║ÄĶ░āĶ»ĢÕÆīµĄŗĶ»Ģ\n- õĖÄ spec õĖŁÕ«Üõ╣ēńÜäń▒╗ń╗ōµ×äÕ«īÕģ©Õī╣ķģŹ\n\n**ń╝║ńé╣**’╝Ü\n- ń▒╗ÕīģÕÉ½ÕżÜń¦ŹĶüīĶ┤Ż’╝łńēłµ£¼ń«ĪńÉåŃĆüµĀĪķ¬īŃĆüµ×äÕ╗║ŃĆüÕģāµĢ░µŹ«µø┤µ¢░’╝ē\n- õ║æń½»µ×äÕ╗║ķĆ╗ĶŠæÕÅ»ĶāĮõĖÄµ£¼Õ£░µ×äÕ╗║ÕĘ«Õ╝éĶŠāÕż¦\n\n**Õå│ńŁ¢**’╝Üķććńö©ŃĆéõĖÄńÄ░µ£ē spec ÕÆī pack ÕæĮõ╗żµ×Čµ×äõĖĆĶć┤’╝īSize M ĶīāÕø┤ÕåģÕÅ»µÄ¦ŃĆé\n\n### 2. µ×äÕ╗║ńŁ¢ńĢźµ©ĪÕ╝ÅÕłåń”╗µ£¼Õ£░/õ║æń½»\n\n**ÕüÜµ│Ģ**’╝ÜÕ«Üõ╣ē `BuildStrategy` µÄźÕÅŻ’╝ī`LocalBuildStrategy` ÕÆī `CloudBuildStrategy` Õ«×ńÄ░’╝ī`BuildRuntime` Õ¦öµēśń╗ÖńŁ¢ńĢźŃĆé\n\n**õ╝śńé╣**’╝Ü\n- µ£¼Õ£░ÕÆīõ║æń½»µ×äÕ╗║ķĆ╗ĶŠæÕ«īÕģ©ķÜöń”╗\n- µĘ╗ÕŖĀµ¢░µ×äÕ╗║µ¢╣Õ╝Å’╝łÕ”é remote Docker daemon’╝ēÕÅ¬ķ£Ćµ¢░ńŁ¢ńĢź\n\n**ń╝║ńé╣**’╝Ü\n- Õó×ÕŖĀµŖĮĶ▒ĪÕ▒é’╝īÕ»╣ÕĮōÕēŹõ╗ģ 2 ń¦Źµ×äÕ╗║µ©ĪÕ╝ÅµØźĶ»┤Ķ┐ćÕ║”Ķ«ŠĶ«Ī\n- õĖÄ spec õĖŁÕ«Üõ╣ēńÜä `_build_local` / `_build_cloud` ń¦üµ£ēµ¢╣µ│Ģń╗ōµ×äõĖŹõĖĆĶć┤\n\n**Õå│ńŁ¢**’╝ÜõĖŹķććńö©ŃĆéÕĮōÕēŹõ╗ģµö»µīü local/cloud’╝īńŁ¢ńĢźµ©ĪÕ╝ÅÕó×ÕŖĀÕżŹµØéÕ║”ŃĆéÕÅ»Õ£©µ£¬µØźµĘ╗ÕŖĀń¼¼ 3 ń¦Źµ×äÕ╗║µ¢╣Õ╝ÅµŚČķćŹµ×äŃĆé\n\n### 3. ńēłµ£¼Ķć¬Õó×µöŠÕ£© pack ķśČµ«Ą\n\n**ÕüÜµ│Ģ**’╝Üpack µŚČÕ░▒ńĪ«Õ«Üńēłµ£¼ÕÅĘ’╝ībuild õĮ┐ńö©Õø║Õ«Üńēłµ£¼ŃĆé\n\n**õ╝śńé╣**’╝Ü\n- ńēłµ£¼ÕÅĘÕ£© pack µŚČńĪ«Õ«Ü’╝ībuild µø┤ń«ĆÕŹĢ\n- ńö©µłĘÕÅ»õ╗źÕ£© pack ÕÉÄķóäĶ¦łńēłµ£¼ÕÅĘ\n\n**ń╝║ńé╣**’╝Ü\n- ÕżÜµ¼Ī build õ╝Üõ║¦ńö¤ńøĖÕÉīńēłµ£¼ÕÅĘńÜäķĢ£ÕāÅ’╝īµŚĀµ│ĢÕī║Õłå\n- Ķ┐ØÕÅŹ\"µ»Åµ¼Īµ×äÕ╗║õ║¦ńö¤Õö»õĖĆõ║¦ńē®\"ńÜäÕÄ¤ÕłÖ\n- õĖÄ spec õĖŁ\"build µŚČĶć¬Õó×ńēłµ£¼\"ńÜäĶ”üµ▒éõĖŹń¼”\n\n**Õå│ńŁ¢**’╝ÜõĖŹķććńö©ŃĆébuild ķśČµ«Ąµ»Åµ¼Īµē¦ĶĪīķāĮńö¤µłÉµ¢░ķĢ£ÕāÅ’╝īńēłµ£¼ÕÅĘÕ║öÕ£© build µŚČĶć¬Õó×ŃĆé\n\n## Õ«×ńÄ░Ķ”üńé╣\n\n### `build` ÕæĮõ╗żµĄüń©ŗ\n\n```python\n@app.command()\ndef build(\n    workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", ...),\n    proxy: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"-p\", \"--proxy\", ...),\n    cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\", ...),\n    output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\", ...),\n    verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", ...),\n) -> None:\n    workspace_path = Path(workspace).resolve()\n    try:\n        with Progress() as progress:\n            task = progress.add_task(\"Building...\", total=None)\n            runtime = BuildRuntime(verbose=verbose)\n            result = runtime.build(workspace_path,\n                proxy=proxy,\n                cloud_provider=cloud_provider,\n                output=output,\n            )\n        # Rich ĶŠōÕć║: image_name, tag, build_time\n    except Exception as e:\n        _handle_error(e, \"build\", verbose)\n```\n\n### `BuildRuntime.build()` Õåģķā©µĄüń©ŗ\n\n```python\ndef build(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    # 1. ÕŖĀĶĮĮÕģāµĢ░µŹ«\n    metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n\n    # 2. Ķć¬Õó×ńēłµ£¼ÕÅĘ\n    original_version = metadata.version\n    self._increment_version(workspace_path, metadata)\n\n    try:\n        # 3. ÕēŹńĮ«µĀĪķ¬ī\n        self._validate_build_prerequisites(workspace_path)\n\n        # 4. µĀ╣µŹ« build_mode ÕłåÕÅæ\n        if metadata.build_mode == \"local\":\n            build_result = self._build_local(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n        else:\n            build_result = self._build_cloud(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n\n        # 5. µø┤µ¢░ÕģāµĢ░µŹ«\n        tag = metadata.version or \"latest\"\n        self._update_build_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, build_result, tag)\n\n        return build_result\n\n    except Exception:\n        # Õø×µ╗Üńēłµ£¼ÕÅĘ\n        metadata.version = original_version\n        self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n        raise\n```\n\n### ńēłµ£¼Ķć¬Õó×ķĆ╗ĶŠæ\n\n```python\ndef _increment_version(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata) -> Any:\n    current = metadata.version\n    if not current:\n        metadata.version = \"0.0.1\"\n    elif re.match(r\"^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$\", current):\n        # X.Y.Z ŌåÆ X.Y.(Z+1)\n        parts = current.split(\".\")\n        parts[2] = str(int(parts[2]) + 1)\n        metadata.version = \".\".join(parts)\n    else:\n        # ķØ×µĀćÕćåµĀ╝Õ╝Å: Ķ┐ĮÕŖĀ .1 µł¢ {version}-1\n        try:\n            v = semver.Version.parse(current)\n            metadata.version = str(v.bump_patch())\n        except ValueError:\n            metadata.version = f\"{current}-1\"\n```\n\n### Docker ÕēŹńĮ«µĀĪķ¬ī\n\n```python\ndef _validate_build_prerequisites(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None:\n    metadata_path = workspace_path / \"agent_metadata.yaml\"\n    if not metadata_path.exists():\n        raise ValueError(f\"Metadata file not found: {metadata_path}\")\n\n    dockerfile_path = workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\"\n    if not dockerfile_path.exists():\n        raise ValueError(\"Dockerfile not found. Run 'pack' first.\")\n\n    docker_service = DockerService(verbose=self.verbose)\n    if not docker_service.check_docker_available():\n        raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n```\n\n### µ£¼Õ£░µ×äÕ╗║Õ«×ńÄ░\n\n```python\ndef _build_local(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    docker_service = DockerService(verbose=self.verbose)\n    image_name = metadata.image.get(\"name\", metadata.agent_name) if metadata.image else metadata.agent_name\n    tag = metadata.version or \"latest\"\n\n    build_args = None\n    if options.get(\"proxy\"):\n        build_args = {\"HTTP_PROXY\": options[\"proxy\"], \"HTTPS_PROXY\": options[\"proxy\"]}\n\n    dockerfile_path = workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\"\n    result = docker_service.build_image(\n        dockerfile_path=dockerfile_path,\n        context_path=workspace_path,\n        image_name=image_name,\n        tag=tag,\n        build_args=build_args,\n    )\n    return result\n```\n\n### `DockerService.check_docker_available()`\n\n```python\ndef check_docker_available(self) -> bool:\n    try:\n        client = docker.from_env()\n        client.ping()\n        return True\n    except Exception:\n        return False\n```\n\n### `DockerService.build_image()`\n\n```python\ndef build_image(self, dockerfile_path: Path, context_path: Path,\n                image_name: str, tag: str = \"latest\",\n                build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None) -> Dict[str, str]:\n    client = docker.from_env()\n    start_time = time.time()\n\n    image, logs = client.images.build(\n        path=str(context_path),\n        dockerfile=str(dockerfile_path),\n        tag=f\"{image_name}:{tag}\",\n        buildargs=build_args,\n    )\n\n    build_time = time.time() - start_time\n    image_info = client.images.get(image.id)\n\n    return {\n        \"image_name\": image_name,\n        \"image_id\": image.short_id,\n        \"image_size\": self._format_size(image_info.attrs.get(\"Size\", 0)),\n        \"build_time\": f\"{build_time:.2f}s\",\n    }\n```\n\n## ķ¬īµöČµĀćÕćå\n\n- [ ] `build` ÕæĮõ╗żµÄźÕÅŚµēĆµ£ēµīćÕ«ÜķĆēķĪ╣’╝īõĮ┐ńö©µŁŻńĪ«ķ╗śĶ«żÕĆ╝\n- [ ] `workspace` ķ╗śĶ«ż `.`’╝īÕÅ»ķĆÜĶ┐ć `-f` / `--workspace` Ķ”åńø¢\n- [ ] `proxy` ÕÅ»ķĆÜĶ┐ć `-p` / `--proxy` µīćÕ«Ü’╝īõĮ£õĖ║ Docker build args õ╝ĀķĆÆ\n- [ ] `build_mode` õĖ║ `local` µŚČ’╝īDocker õĖŹÕÅ»ńö©µŖøÕć║ `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")`\n- [ ] `build_mode` õĖ║ `local` µŚČ’╝īDockerfile õĖŹÕŁśÕ£©µŖøÕć║µśÄńĪ«ķöÖĶ»»µÅÉńż║\n- [ ] ńēłµ£¼ÕÅĘĶć¬Õó×’╝Ü`X.Y.Z` ŌåÆ `X.Y.(Z+1)`’╝øµŚĀńēłµ£¼ ŌåÆ `0.0.1`’╝øķØ×µĀćÕćåµĀ╝Õ╝Å fallback\n- [ ] µ×äÕ╗║Õż▒Ķ┤źµŚČńēłµ£¼ÕÅĘÕø×µ╗ÜÕł░ÕÄ¤Õ¦ŗÕĆ╝\n- [ ] µ×äÕ╗║µłÉÕŖ¤ÕÉÄµø┤µ¢░ `metadata.image` ÕŁŚµ«Ą’╝łimage_name, image_id, tag’╝ē\n- [ ] µłÉÕŖ¤µČłµü»µśŠńż║ķĢ£ÕāÅÕÉŹń¦░ŃĆüµĀćńŁŠŃĆüµ×äÕ╗║µŚČķŚ┤’╝łRich µĀ╝Õ╝Å’╝ē\n- [ ] ķöÖĶ»»ÕżäńÉåµēōÕŹ░ń║óĶē▓µČłµü» + traceback’╝łverbose’╝ē’╝īķĆĆÕć║ńĀü 1\n- [ ] Rich `Progress` spinner Õ£©µē¦ĶĪīµ£¤ķŚ┤µśŠńż║\n- [ ] `--verbose` ÕÉ»ńö©Ķ»”ń╗åµŚźÕ┐ŚĶŠōÕć║\n- [ ] `cloud_provider` ķĆēķĪ╣Õ£© cloud µ©ĪÕ╝ÅõĖŗńö¤µĢł’╝łÕÅ»õ╝ĀÕÅéń╗Öõ║æń½»µ×äÕ╗║’╝ē\n- [ ] `--output` ķĆēķĪ╣µö»µīüµīćÕ«Üµ×äÕ╗║õ║¦ńē®ĶŠōÕć║ĶĘ»ÕŠä\n\n## ńŖČµĆü\n\n- [ ] µÅÉµĪłÕ«Īµ¤ź\n- [ ] Õ«×ńÄ░\n- [ ] ķ¬īĶ»ü\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/proposal.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775852030989,"end":1775852031015}}}}
